text.tspan: This weekend, we will hack an A/C remote. The
goal is to control the A/C over WiFi. The circuit has
an infrared diode and WiFi, replaying the radio
signals to the A/C unit. In theory, you can control
any Ir-remote device. In the workshop, we will
learn how a remote works, and see the signals to
